wiki.content: "Work" is a song recorded by Australian hip hop recording artist Iggy Azalea, from her upcoming debut studio album The New Classic. The song was released as her debut single, and the lead single on March 17, 2013 through Mercury Records. It was written by Iggy Azalea and Natalie Sims, and produced by 1st Down and The Invisible Men. Musically, "Work" is an up-tempo alternative hip-hop song with an electronic sound.
